select distinct ?a ?b ?la ?lb where {?a bksport:playFor ?b . ?a rdfs:label ?la . ?b rdfs:label ?lb }

column3: select ?a where { ?b bksport:about <A> . ?b rdf:type bksport:News . ?b bksport:hasURL ?a }
